## 🏍️ Supported Bikes

Pre-loaded with ARAI certified base mileage figures:

| Bike | Base kmpl | CC |
|------|-----------|-----|
| Honda Activa | 60 | 110 |
| Hero Splendor | 65 | 100 |
| Hero HF Deluxe | 67 | 100 |
| Bajaj Pulsar 150 | 45 | 150 |
| Royal Enfield 350 | 30 | 350 |
| Yamaha R15 | 40 | 155 |
| KTM Duke 200 | 35 | 200 |
| Ola S1 Pro | 80 | EV |
| Ather 450X | 85 | EV |

**Custom Bikes:** You can also type any bike name and enter your own base kmpl manually.

---

## ⚠️ Known Limitations

- **GPS Speed:** Requires outdoor use — indoors shows 0 kmph
- **iOS Sensor:** Requires HTTPS (Android works on HTTP)
- **Jerk Calculation:** Needs at least 2 consecutive readings to be accurate
- **Mileage Model:** Trained on Nairobi data — speed patterns may differ slightly for Indian highways

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Component | Technology |
|-----------|------------|
| **Backend** | Python, Flask, FastAPI |
| **ML/AI** | XGBoost, Scikit-learn, SHAP, Optuna |
| **Frontend** | Vanilla HTML/CSS/JS (no framework) |
| **Sensors** | Web DeviceMotion API (accelerometer + gyroscope) |
| **GPS** | Web Geolocation API |

